These specialized materials promise enhanced strength, reduced shrinkage, and better heat resistance—but how do they really perform? In this video, I explore everything from unboxing to hands-on 3D printing and real-world stress tests. I evaluate key aspects like layer adhesion, tensile strength, impact resistance, and more. I even dive into thermal performance and long-term creep behavior to see which filament is the ultimate choice for demanding applications. Whether you're a maker, engineer, or hobbyist, this comprehensive review will help you decide which filament suits your needs.
